WEBVTT

00:00:19.162 --> 00:00:24.349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:25.661
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.662 --> 00:00:27.741
♪You're always♪

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:32.391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.392 --> 00:00:35.124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.125 --> 00:00:36.691
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:36.692 --> 00:00:42.481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.995
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 18=

00:00:48.979 --> 00:00:51.298
The arrangements
for the auction are almost done.

00:00:51.299 --> 00:00:52.579
Please rest assured, Ms. Xu.

00:00:53.659 --> 00:00:54.659
Not bad.

00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:56.460
I haven't misjudged you.

00:00:56.939 --> 00:00:59.299
But there's one more thing
I want to ask you, Ms. Xu.

00:01:00.659 --> 00:01:01.859
For this auction,

00:01:01.860 --> 00:01:03.698
Mu Zhiyu is personally in charge.

00:01:03.699 --> 00:01:05.900
To stabilize your position in the group,

00:01:06.339 --> 00:01:08.099
I can use some methods

00:01:08.499 --> 00:01:10.260
to make her leave Mu Group.

00:01:12.380 --> 00:01:14.418
Now I'm just hoping
you two will get married soon

00:01:14.419 --> 00:01:16.257
so you can inherit the estate smoothly.

00:01:16.850 --> 00:01:18.610
Then, you'll take
advantage of the situation

00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.399
and snatch the inheritance

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:21.759
that Mu Zhiyu receives from her.

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:24.900
You should focus your mind

00:01:24.979 --> 00:01:26.860
on getting married and having kids.

00:01:32.740 --> 00:01:36.140
(Success is near,
I cannot let my guard down.)

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:39.322
(Back then, I swapped
Shen Yi and Mu Chenzhou's son.)

00:01:39.512 --> 00:01:42.058
(If Shen Yi hadn't kept calling,
saying she missed her daughter,)

00:01:42.059 --> 00:01:44.019
(I wouldn't have had
to force them to go abroad.)

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:45.579
(This is great.)

00:01:45.580 --> 00:01:46.840
(One died of depression,)

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:49.080
(and the other died a violent death
on the streets fighting.)

00:01:50.059 --> 00:01:52.179
(Now, everyone in the way is dead.)

00:01:52.687 --> 00:01:54.647
(There are no more worries.)

00:02:05.450 --> 00:02:08.331
(Jibai, I have a plan next.)

00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:12.939
(It might be a little hard on you.)

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:16.500
Shen Jibai,

00:02:16.779 --> 00:02:18.859
you really have been
lying to me all along.

00:02:19.900 --> 00:02:21.459
Is there some kind of misunderstanding?

00:02:21.460 --> 00:02:22.220
Misunderstanding?

00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:30.580
I always thought

00:02:31.219 --> 00:02:33.979
you truly wanted
to help me and cooperate with me.

00:02:34.779 --> 00:02:37.139
Actually, you've been
acting this whole time, right?

00:02:38.099 --> 00:02:39.300
From beginning to end,

00:02:39.420 --> 00:02:41.259
it's been a scam
between you and Xu Mingzhu.

00:02:41.260 --> 00:02:41.419
I...

00:02:41.420 --> 00:02:42.899
The goal was to seize Mu Group.

00:02:42.900 --> 00:02:43.900
And I...

00:02:47.580 --> 00:02:50.020
I'm nothing but a pawn you used.

00:02:55.779 --> 00:02:57.220
I always thought

00:02:57.740 --> 00:03:00.180
you were someone worthy of my trust.

00:03:01.020 --> 00:03:02.220
But I didn't know

00:03:04.740 --> 00:03:05.939
the result would be the same.

00:03:08.980 --> 00:03:10.099
Shen Jibai,

00:03:11.125 --> 00:03:13.761
you keep telling me
about your sincerity,

00:03:13.762 --> 00:03:16.404
but the fact is,
I don't know you at all.

00:03:19.499 --> 00:03:21.819
A relationship
requires respect and trust.

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:24.300
But did you do that?

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:31.459
Zhiyu, just give me a little more time.

00:03:31.460 --> 00:03:33.419
I will definitely
explain everything to you.

00:03:34.980 --> 00:03:36.259
Explain?

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:39.058
You told me long ago

00:03:39.059 --> 00:03:40.859
that you'd explain
everything clearly to me.

00:03:42.219 --> 00:03:43.220
And now?

00:03:44.379 --> 00:03:45.580
Have you explained?

00:03:47.379 --> 00:03:48.539
I don't want to wait anymore.

00:03:49.140 --> 00:03:50.099
It doesn't matter now.

00:03:52.219 --> 00:03:53.780
At tomorrow's engagement ceremony,

00:03:54.099 --> 00:03:54.818
I will choose

00:03:54.819 --> 00:03:56.740
an engagement partner
who is worthy of my trust.

00:03:57.860 --> 00:03:58.819
Don't worry.

00:03:59.580 --> 00:04:01.740
I won't let your conspiracy succeed.

00:04:16.900 --> 00:04:17.778
Don't be nervous.

00:04:17.779 --> 00:04:18.940
It's just for show.

00:04:20.179 --> 00:04:21.020
I know.

00:04:21.380 --> 00:04:23.299
It's fake, we're acting.

00:04:23.500 --> 00:04:25.460
But the more realistic the acting,

00:04:25.500 --> 00:04:26.940
the better the effect, right?

00:04:30.662 --> 00:04:32.218
(This darn girl.)

00:04:32.219 --> 00:04:34.299
(I don't know what's gotten into her.)

00:04:34.659 --> 00:04:35.978
(Suddenly giving up on Shen Jibai)

00:04:35.979 --> 00:04:38.220
(and turning around
to get together with He Min.)

00:04:38.419 --> 00:04:39.699
(That's fine, too.)

00:04:39.700 --> 00:04:42.220
(He Min is easier to control
than Shen Jibai.)

00:04:42.512 --> 00:04:44.795
(Wait until I get the inheritance
and take over the company.)

00:04:45.175 --> 00:04:47.049
(Then you fake couple)

00:04:47.050 --> 00:04:49.157
(can both get out
of the Mu family together.)

00:04:49.820 --> 00:04:52.020
Friends and family,

00:04:52.140 --> 00:04:53.499
good morning everyone.

00:04:53.580 --> 00:04:55.580
The engagement ceremony begins now.

00:04:55.620 --> 00:04:58.700
Next, please welcome
our two newcomers to the stage.

00:04:59.500 --> 00:04:59.978
Good.

00:04:59.979 --> 00:05:01.900
That's great. Really great.

00:05:02.260 --> 00:05:02.940
Wait!

00:05:14.859 --> 00:05:15.859
Shen Jibai.

00:05:20.460 --> 00:05:21.099
Hey!

00:05:23.179 --> 00:05:24.059
Shen Jibai.

00:05:25.820 --> 00:05:26.739
Shen Jibai.

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:28.739
Shen Jibai, you!

00:05:42.739 --> 00:05:43.819
Shen Jibai.

00:05:43.820 --> 00:05:45.659
Shen Jibai, what on earth are you doing?

00:05:46.299 --> 00:05:48.019
Are you really going
to get engaged to He Min?

00:05:48.020 --> 00:05:49.020
What if I am?

00:06:34.712 --> 00:06:40.124
♪There is a void in my chest♪

00:06:40.125 --> 00:06:43.586
♪Your freedom♪

00:06:43.587 --> 00:06:48.895
♪Has become my prison♪

00:06:49.050 --> 00:06:55.795
♪My hand brushed across the smile
on the photo♪

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:58.539
Shen Jibai,

00:06:59.620 --> 00:07:00.940
what exactly do you want?

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:02.780
Didn't you tell me

00:07:03.620 --> 00:07:04.419
that love

00:07:06.419 --> 00:07:08.340
requires respect and trust?

00:07:08.387 --> 00:07:10.538
♪You told me♪

00:07:10.539 --> 00:07:11.859
It was I who failed to do that.

00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:15.380
But I promise you,

00:07:16.060 --> 00:07:18.099
from now on,
I will let you know more about me

00:07:18.779 --> 00:07:20.299
and give you
a sufficient sense of trust.

00:07:22.412 --> 00:07:24.070
Do the things you were hiding from me

00:07:24.525 --> 00:07:26.086
have something to do with your mom?

00:07:26.087 --> 00:07:31.836
♪When I look up at the distant stars♪

00:07:31.837 --> 00:07:35.832
♪Everything is hazy♪

00:07:36.339 --> 00:07:37.739
What clues did you find?

00:07:38.859 --> 00:07:40.340
Your mother, Shen Yi,

00:07:40.979 --> 00:07:42.418
once worked as a caregiver

00:07:42.419 --> 00:07:43.739
when my grandfather was sick,

00:07:44.179 --> 00:07:45.499
right up until he passed away.

00:07:46.659 --> 00:07:47.940
That jade pendant

00:07:48.940 --> 00:07:50.380
was also taken by your mother.

00:07:53.299 --> 00:07:54.580
- I think...
- Shen Jibai,

00:07:54.739 --> 00:07:55.899
respect and trust

00:07:55.900 --> 00:07:57.140
are mutual.

00:07:57.380 --> 00:07:58.419
I trust you,

00:08:00.060 --> 00:08:01.539
and you must trust me, too.

00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:06.700
I know.

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:08.899
The reason you're still
by Xu Mingzhu's side

00:08:08.900 --> 00:08:09.940
is that

00:08:10.859 --> 00:08:12.580
you're afraid she'll do something to me.

00:08:13.099 --> 00:08:14.380
You want to protect me.

00:08:14.940 --> 00:08:16.020
But now,

00:08:17.237 --> 00:08:19.419
we must tear off her mask.

00:08:19.862 --> 00:08:21.502
So, you got engaged to He Min

00:08:23.979 --> 00:08:25.778
just to make Xu Mingzhu
think we've fallen out,

00:08:25.779 --> 00:08:26.979
sabotage her plans,

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.460
and force her to show her true colors?

00:08:35.020 --> 00:08:36.799
Only when people are desperate

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:38.482
will they risk everything.

00:08:39.459 --> 00:08:40.899
We must use this

00:08:41.140 --> 00:08:42.420
to make Xu Mingzhu

00:08:42.579 --> 00:08:44.220
expose her own conspiracy.

00:08:49.179 --> 00:08:51.340
Actually, I also have a plan

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:53.619
to expose Xu Mingzhu

00:08:55.419 --> 00:08:57.019
and get her out of the Mu family sooner.

00:09:02.579 --> 00:09:03.859
Ms. Xu,

00:09:04.059 --> 00:09:07.060
when exactly is this
opening ceremony starting?

00:09:07.260 --> 00:09:10.099
We're all still waiting to see the concept art for
"Changing Mountains and Rivers".

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:11.658
Please be patient.

00:09:11.659 --> 00:09:12.899
As soon as we're ready,

00:09:12.900 --> 00:09:14.460
we will begin immediately.

00:09:15.160 --> 00:09:17.019
- Just wait a little longer.
- It's been so long.

00:09:17.020 --> 00:09:18.060
Yeah.

00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:20.619
(The Mu Group will soon be mine.)

00:09:21.175 --> 00:09:22.735
(Nothing must go wrong.)

00:09:24.179 --> 00:09:26.379
With Hong's exclusive auction
approaching,

00:09:26.699 --> 00:09:28.499
a large number of

00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:30.300
counterfeit paintings
have been discovered.

00:09:31.179 --> 00:09:33.139
Look at the news.
Something happened to Hong.

00:09:33.140 --> 00:09:34.180
(The plan has begun.)

00:09:34.340 --> 00:09:37.818
Regarding the news that Mr. Hong's works
have been maliciously forged

00:09:37.819 --> 00:09:39.840
and that fakes have entered the market,

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:42.418
our studio is currently investigating
and will hand it over to the court soon.

00:09:42.419 --> 00:09:44.820
(I hope this takes down Xu Mingzhu.)

00:09:44.939 --> 00:09:46.739
We have only
collaborated with the Mu Group.

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:48.099
(How could this happen?)

00:09:48.100 --> 00:09:49.899
(Who is behind this?)

00:09:49.900 --> 00:09:51.979
The works only passed
through us and the Mu Group.

00:09:52.059 --> 00:09:53.538
So during the investigation,

00:09:53.539 --> 00:09:54.538
we have decided

00:09:54.539 --> 00:09:56.940
to suspend all cooperation
with the Mu Group.

00:09:57.719 --> 00:09:59.139
- What about the paintings?
- Exactly!

00:10:02.100 --> 00:10:03.220
(This is bad.)

00:10:03.260 --> 00:10:05.940
(If negative news hits the auction,)

00:10:05.980 --> 00:10:07.899
(it's not just
the Mu Group's reputation.)

00:10:08.140 --> 00:10:09.899
(If their marriage falls through,)

00:10:09.900 --> 00:10:11.859
(the inheritance conditions
won't be met,)

00:10:11.980 --> 00:10:14.099
(and all my plans will be wasted.)

00:10:14.340 --> 00:10:15.899
Who is making these fakes?

00:10:15.900 --> 00:10:17.099
Seriously!

00:10:22.100 --> 00:10:23.180
My guests,

00:10:23.299 --> 00:10:26.019
I am Xu Mingzhu,
Acting President of Mu Group.

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:26.940
I would like

00:10:27.020 --> 00:10:28.340
to apologize to everyone here.

00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:30.818
Regarding Hong's works,

00:10:30.819 --> 00:10:33.178
the Mu Group will actively cooperate.

00:10:33.179 --> 00:10:34.779
We will give you an explanation soon.

00:10:35.220 --> 00:10:36.058
I hereby

00:10:36.059 --> 00:10:38.300
solemnly state on behalf of the Mu Group

00:10:38.579 --> 00:10:39.859
that we will strictly investigate

00:10:39.860 --> 00:10:41.940
all personnel involved in this auction

00:10:42.419 --> 00:10:43.778
to find the black sheep

00:10:43.779 --> 00:10:46.019
trying to damage
the Mu Group's reputation.

00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:47.019
Wait.

00:10:59.375 --> 00:11:03.605
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:11:03.745 --> 00:11:08.114
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:11:08.115 --> 00:11:12.605
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:11:16.825 --> 00:11:20.764
♪Shadows move around♪

00:11:20.765 --> 00:11:25.374
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:11:25.375 --> 00:11:29.905
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:11:33.505 --> 00:11:39.295
♪Don't slip away♪

00:11:41.745 --> 00:11:46.314
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:46.315 --> 00:11:50.714
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:50.715 --> 00:11:55.035
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:55.055 --> 00:11:59.035
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:59.505 --> 00:12:03.814
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:03.815 --> 00:12:08.144
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:08.145 --> 00:12:12.454
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:12:12.455 --> 00:12:18.605
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪